Title: Forward Camp
Description:
Since Sarkareth now wields the power of Aberrus's defenses, he has an army that will shield him from us.

The next step for us will be to establish a stronghold inside the garrison. That way we can search it without interruption. 

Meet me there.
ObjectivesText: Find Ebyssian in the Brimstone Garrison.

Objectives.Text: Meet Ebyssian at the Brimstone Garrison
